These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, grey
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk
1. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Color   | grey | orange |
| Beverage     | almond-milk    | milk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, yellow
There 2 different types of food: spinach, onion
1. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Color   | yellow | apricot        |
| Food      | spinach  | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, video-games
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall
1. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Hobby   | video-games    | sudoku |
| Cigar   | dannemann | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, engineer
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the engineer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Flower   | sunflower      | rose |
| Job       | librarian | engineer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
