 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rat
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk
1. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Pet       | rat | mouse  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | fanta |

 #################################

 
