.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, fishing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, gospel
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Hobby   | fishing | photography   |
| Music-Genre         | pop | gospel |

